# Scopes

Authored commands should have scopes to keep the editor manageable.

## Global Commands

Available everywhere.

Examples:

```md
pray
sing
wait
listen
inventory
```

## Room Commands

Only available in a specific room.

Examples:

```md
touch mural
listen at door
open curtains
crawl under bed
```

## Feature Commands

Attached to room features.

Examples:

```md
examine table
clean table
move painting
read inscription
```

## Item Commands

Attached to items.

Examples:

```md
eat apple
light lantern
shake bottle
wind music box
```

## NPC Commands

Attached to NPCs.

Examples:

```md
ask cook about rats
give apple to cook
threaten guard
