# Tags

Tags make authoring much more flexible.

Entities should support tags:

```md
food
weapon
key
container
surface
flammable
metal
wooden
fragile
heavy
npc
animal
rat
lightSource
valuable
questItem
```

## Tag Conditions

```md
Target has tag
Object has tag
Inventory contains item with tag
Room contains item with tag
NPC has item with tag
```

## Tag Effects

```md
Remove all items with tag
Move all items with tag
Reveal all objects with tag
Hide all objects with tag
```

## Scenario Example: Any Food Attracts Rats

Instead of only apple:

```md
Command:
put [food] on table

Conditions:
- object has tag food
- target is kitchen table

Effects:
- Place object on table
- Set flag kitchen.foodOnTable true
- Schedule ratsArrive after 3 turns
```

This supports:

```md
put apple on table
put cheese on table
put bread on table
```

